H0.text: Which is the largest borough in New York City. Manhattan

H1.text: Which is the largest borough in New York City. Brooklyn

H2.text: Which is the largest borough in New York City. The Bronx

H3.text: Which is the largest borough in New York City. Queens

A4.text: Manhattan is the most densely populated and geographically smallest of the five boroughs of New York City.

A5.text: Manhattan is the smallest county by area in the U.S. state of New York, and one of the smallest in the United States.

A6.text: The Bronx has the fourth-largest area, fourth-highest population, and third-highest population density of the boroughs.
